Definition: causing or marked by grief or anguish
Example: a grievous loss; a grievous cry; her sigh was heartbreaking; the heartrending words of Rabin's granddaughter
Synonyms: heartbreaking, heartrending, causing, or, marked, by, grief, anguish, a, loss, cry, her, sigh, was, the, words, of, Rabin, s, granddaughter
Category: adj.all
